title: Daisy Moo's Bakehouse
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Take-out, Bakery, British, English
description: Vegetarian bakehouse serving bakery goods, light lunch food, coffee and beverages, since Jun 2014. Sample menu items include falafel, houmous with tascas, sandwiches, soups, ploughman's lunch, sweet and savory scones, gluten-free cakes, and cakes suitable for diabetics. Provides daily newspapers, BT Wi-Fi hotspot with hotdesk facility.
